@startuml

title AI Agent Pipeline (Marketing Agent) - End-to-End

left to right direction
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam roundcorner 12
skinparam packageStyle rectangle

legend right
MainFlow: solid arrow (runtime request/response)
Dependency: dashed arrow (config/data dependency)
Optional: dotted arrow (available but not used by default UI)
endlegend

frame "Stage 0\nUser & Frontend (Implemented)" as Stage0 {
  actor User as User
  rectangle "Vite Frontend\n3-step questionnaire\n- Ad Info\n- Budget\n- Target Audience\n\nBuild question string:\n\"Ad Info: ...\\nBudget: ...\\nTarget Audience: ...\"" as Frontend
}

frame "Stage 1\nAPI Layer - Flask (Implemented)" as Stage1 {
  rectangle "/api/agent\nreturn { reply, raw }" as ApiAgent
  rectangle "/agent\n(debug: raw run_agent result)" as ApiDebug
  rectangle "/api/advice-chat\n(pure LLM chat)\nOptional endpoint" as ApiAdvice
  rectangle "/health\nstatus ok" as ApiHealth
}

frame "Stage 2\nAgent Orchestrator (Implemented)" as Stage2 {
  rectangle "run_agent(question)\nOrchestrate: plan -> tools -> synthesis" as RunAgent

  rectangle "get_llm()\nSelect backend via config.LLM_BACKEND" as GetLLM
  rectangle "_get_default_retriever()\nConditional: enabled when CORPUS_PATH exists" as GetRetriever

  artifact "tool_registry\n- platform_chooser (required)\n- rag (if retriever available)" as ToolRegistry

  rectangle "route_question(question, llm)\nLLM planner -> plan JSON" as Router
  note right of Router
    Plan constraints (Implemented):
    - 1x platform_chooser
    - 2..5x rag steps (capped to MAX_RAG_STEPS)
    - fallback plan if JSON/schema parse fails
  end note

  artifact "plan.json\n[{tool,args}, ...]" as PlanJson

  rectangle "run_plan(plan, tool_registry)\nExecute sequentially\nError-tolerant: tool failure\nwon't stop later steps" as RunPlan
  artifact "trace[]\n{ tool, args, result,\n  result_preview }" as Trace

  rectangle "synthesize_answer(question, trace, llm)\nGenerate structured ad plan\nMarkdown + citations [doc_id]" as Synthesizer
  note right of Synthesizer
    Synthesis rules (Implemented):
    - Use ONLY tool outputs (no fabricated numbers)
    - Sections:
      1.Platform Selection
      2.Budget Allocation
      3.Target Audience
      4.Ad Formats
      5.Key Compliance Points
      6.Execution Recommendations
    - If RAG evidence exists, add [doc_id] citations
  end note
}

frame "Stage 3\nTools (Implemented)" as Stage3 {
  rectangle "platform_chooser(industry, region=US, include_audience=true)\nReturn:\n- platform KPIs (CPC/CPM/CPA, CTR, CVR)\n- audience insights" as PlatformChooser <<tool>>

  rectangle "rag_tool(question, k=3)\nRAG answer + evidence[]\nReturn:\n{ answer, evidence[{doc_id,title,...}] }" as RagTool <<tool>>
}

frame "Stage 4\nData & Models (Implemented + Conditional)" as Stage4 {
  rectangle "config.py + .env\n- LLM_BACKEND\n- API keys / model names\n- CORPUS_PATH / EMBED_MODEL_NAME\n- RAG_TOP_K\n- BENCHMARKS_DIR\n- HF_HOME (cache path)" as Config

  rectangle "LLM Backend\n- OpenAI (remote)\n- HuggingFace (local/remote)\n\nllm.generate(messages,\nmax_new_tokens, temperature)" as LLMBackend <<LLM>>

  database "Benchmarks CSV\n(data/benchmarks/*.csv)\nMeta + Google industry KPIs\nAudience behavior stats" as Benchmarks <<data>>

  database "RAG Corpus JSONL\n(data/corpus/*.jsonl)\nPolicy/knowledge documents" as Corpus <<data>>

  rectangle "VectorStore + Retriever\n(load -> embed -> index)\nretriever.invoke(query) -> top-k docs" as Retriever <<data>>
}

frame "Stage 5\nFinal Output (Implemented)" as Stage5 {
  rectangle "Final Ad Plan (Markdown)\n- structured sections\n- compliance points\n- recommendations\n- citations: [doc_id]\n\nAPI response:\n{ reply, raw{ question, plan, trace, final_answer } }" as FinalOutput
}

' -------- Main runtime flow (solid) --------
User --> Frontend : fill form
Frontend --> ApiAgent : POST /api/agent\n{ question }
ApiAgent --> RunAgent : run_agent(question)

RunAgent --> GetLLM
RunAgent --> GetRetriever
RunAgent --> ToolRegistry

RunAgent --> Router : plan = route_question(...)
Router --> PlanJson
PlanJson --> RunPlan

RunPlan --> PlatformChooser : step 1
RunPlan --> RagTool : steps 2..N

RunPlan --> Trace : append results
Trace --> Synthesizer
Synthesizer --> RunAgent : final_answer

RunAgent --> ApiAgent : raw result
ApiAgent --> Frontend : { reply, raw }
Frontend --> User : show structured plan

Synthesizer --> FinalOutput : reply (final_answer)
ApiAgent --> FinalOutput : raw (plan + trace)

' -------- Optional endpoints (dotted) --------
Frontend ..> ApiAdvice : (optional)\nPOST /api/advice-chat\n{messages[]}
ApiAdvice ..> GetLLM : get_llm()
ApiAdvice ..> LLMBackend : llm.generate(...)

ApiDebug ..> RunAgent : (optional)\nPOST /agent\n{question}

' -------- Dependencies (dashed) --------
Config ..> GetLLM
Config ..> GetRetriever
Config ..> PlatformChooser
Config ..> RagTool

PlatformChooser ..> Benchmarks : read/aggregate
GetRetriever ..> Retriever : build/load index
Retriever ..> Corpus : load docs
GetLLM ..> LLMBackend : select backend/model
RagTool ..> Retriever : retrieve top-k docs
RagTool ..> LLMBackend : generate grounded answer
Synthesizer ..> LLMBackend : generate final plan

note bottom of Stage4
RAG is conditional:
- If CORPUS_PATH is not set / corpus missing -> retriever not built -> rag tool not registered.
In that case, pipeline still works with platform_chooser + synthesis (with fewer citations).
end note

@enduml
